SELECT AVG(UserID) FROM sparkhits;
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT UserID) FROM sparkhits;
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT SearchPhrase) FROM sparkhits;
SELECT MIN(EventDate), MAX(EventDate) FROM sparkhits;
SELECT AdvEngineID, COUNT(*) FROM sparkhits WHERE AdvEngineID <> 0 GROUP BY AdvEngineID ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC;
SELECT RegionID, COUNT(DISTINCT UserID) AS u FROM sparkhits GROUP BY RegionID ORDER BY u DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT RegionID, SUM(AdvEngineID), COUNT(*) AS c, AVG(ResolutionWidth), COUNT(DISTINCT UserID) FROM sparkhits GROUP BY RegionID ORDER BY c DESC LIMIT 10;

SELECT MobilePhone, MobilePhoneModel, COUNT(DISTINCT UserID) AS u FROM sparkhits WHERE MobilePhoneModel <> '' GROUP BY MobilePhone, MobilePhoneModel ORDER BY u DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT SearchPhrase, COUNT(*) AS c FROM sparkhits WHERE SearchPhrase <> '' GROUP BY SearchPhrase ORDER BY c DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT SearchPhrase, COUNT(DISTINCT UserID) AS u FROM sparkhits WHERE SearchPhrase <> '' GROUP BY SearchPhrase ORDER BY u DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT SearchEngineID, SearchPhrase, COUNT(*) AS c FROM sparkhits WHERE SearchPhrase <> '' GROUP BY SearchEngineID, SearchPhrase ORDER BY c DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT UserID, COUNT(*) FROM sparkhits GROUP BY UserID ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT UserID, SearchPhrase, COUNT(*) FROM sparkhits GROUP BY UserID, SearchPhrase ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT UserID, SearchPhrase, COUNT(*) FROM sparkhits GROUP BY UserID, SearchPhrase LIMIT 10;

SELECT UserID, extract(minute FROM TIMESTAMP(EventTime)) AS m, SearchPhrase, COUNT(*) FROM sparkhits GROUP BY UserID, extract(minute FROM TIMESTAMP(EventTime)), SearchPhrase ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT UserID FROM sparkhits WHERE UserID = 435090932899640449;
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM sparkhits WHERE URL LIKE '%google%';
SELECT SearchPhrase, MIN(URL), COUNT(*) AS c FROM sparkhits WHERE URL LIKE '%google%' AND SearchPhrase <> '' GROUP BY SearchPhrase ORDER BY c DESC LIMIT 10;

SELECT SearchPhrase, MIN(URL), MIN(Title), COUNT(*) AS c, COUNT(DISTINCT UserID) FROM sparkhits WHERE Title LIKE '%Google%' AND URL NOT LIKE '%.google.%' AND SearchPhrase <> '' GROUP BY SearchPhrase ORDER BY c DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT * FROM sparkhits WHERE URL LIKE '%google%' ORDER BY EventTime LIMIT 10;
SELECT SearchPhrase FROM sparkhits WHERE SearchPhrase <> '' ORDER BY EventTime LIMIT 10;
SELECT SearchPhrase FROM sparkhits WHERE SearchPhrase <> '' ORDER BY SearchPhrase LIMIT 10;
SELECT SearchPhrase FROM sparkhits WHERE SearchPhrase <> '' ORDER BY EventTime, SearchPhrase LIMIT 10;
SELECT CounterID, AVG(length(URL)) AS l, COUNT(*) AS c FROM sparkhits WHERE URL <> '' GROUP BY CounterID HAVING COUNT(*) > 100000 ORDER BY l DESC LIMIT 25;

SELECT REGEXP_REPLACE(Referer, '^https?://(?:www\.)?([^/]+)/.*$', '\1') AS k, AVG(length(Referer)) AS l, COUNT(*) AS c, MIN(Referer) FROM sparkhits WHERE Referer <> '' GROUP BY REGEXP_REPLACE(Referer, '^https?://(?:www\.)?([^/]+)/.*$', '\1') HAVING COUNT(*) > 100000 ORDER BY l DESC LIMIT 25;

SELECT URL, COUNT(*) AS PageViews FROM sparkhits WHERE CounterID = 62 AND EventDate >= 15887 AND EventDate <= 15917 AND DontCountHits = 0 AND IsRefresh = 0 AND URL <> '' GROUP BY URL ORDER BY PageViews DESC LIMIT 10;

SELECT Title, COUNT(*) AS PageViews FROM sparkhits WHERE CounterID = 62 AND EventDate >= 15887 AND EventDate <= 15917 AND DontCountHits = 0 AND IsRefresh = 0 AND Title <> '' GROUP BY Title ORDER BY PageViews DESC LIMIT 10;

SELECT URL, COUNT(*) AS PageViews FROM sparkhits WHERE CounterID = 62 AND EventDate >= 15887 AND EventDate <= 15917 AND IsRefresh = 0 AND IsLink <> 0 AND IsDownload = 0 GROUP BY URL ORDER BY PageViews DESC LIMIT 1010;

SELECT TraficSourceID, SearchEngineID, AdvEngineID, CASE WHEN (SearchEngineID = 0 AND AdvEngineID = 0) THEN Referer ELSE '' END AS Src, URL AS Dst, COUNT(*) AS PageViews FROM sparkhits WHERE CounterID = 62 AND EventDate >= 15887 AND EventDate <= 15917 AND IsRefresh = 0 GROUP BY TraficSourceID, SearchEngineID, AdvEngineID, CASE WHEN (SearchEngineID = 0 AND AdvEngineID = 0) THEN Referer ELSE '' END, URL ORDER BY PageViews DESC LIMIT 1010;

SELECT URLHash, EventDate, COUNT(*) AS PageViews FROM sparkhits WHERE CounterID = 62 AND EventDate >= 15887 AND EventDate <= 15917 AND IsRefresh = 0 AND TraficSourceID IN (-1, 6) AND RefererHash = 3594120000172545465 GROUP BY URLHash, EventDate ORDER BY PageViews DESC LIMIT 110;

SELECT WindowClientWidth, WindowClientHeight, COUNT(*) AS PageViews FROM sparkhits WHERE CounterID = 62 AND EventDate >= 15887 AND EventDate <= 15917 AND IsRefresh = 0 AND DontCountHits = 0 AND URLHash = 2868770270353813622 GROUP BY WindowClientWidth, WindowClientHeight ORDER BY PageViews DESC LIMIT 10010;

SELECT DATE_TRUNC('minute', TIMESTAMP(EventTime)) AS M, COUNT(*) AS PageViews FROM sparkhits WHERE CounterID = 62 AND EventDate >= 15900 AND EventDate <= 15901 AND IsRefresh = 0 AND DontCountHits = 0 GROUP BY DATE_TRUNC('minute', TIMESTAMP(EventTime)) ORDER BY DATE_TRUNC('minute', TIMESTAMP(EventTime)) LIMIT 1010;
